container.startup_command: git clone {{GIT_ADDRESS}} ./; if [[ ! -z ${NODE_PACKAGES} ]]; then /usr/local/bin/npm install ${NODE_PACKAGES}; fi; if [[ ! -z ${UNNODE_PACKAGES} ]]; then /usr/local/bin/npm uninstall ${UNNODE_PACKAGES}; fi; if [ -f /home/container/package.json ]; then /usr/local/bin/npm install; fi; if [ /home/container/{{JS_FILE}} ]; then /usr/local/bin/node /home/container/{{JS_FILE}}; fi;
